    {
      "text": "\nFact-checking the Supreme Court ruling on abortion\n",
      "url": "/article/2022/jun/24/fact-checking-5-claims-final-supreme-court-ruling-/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nJim Lamon\n",
      "url": "/personalities/jim-lamon/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nBlake Masters \u201cunironically quoted a Nazi, called World War II an unjust war, called the Unabomber one of his intellectual influencers, and shared an article attacking Israel as the North Korea of the Middle East.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/16/jim-lamon/arizona-us-senate-race-attack-ties-masters-nazis-u/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nTed Cruz\n",
      "url": "/personalities/ted-cruz/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\"The impact of President Biden being beholden to the Green New Deal radicals in his party has electricity costs through the roof in Texas.\"\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/21/ted-cruz/green-new-deal-not-blame-high-electricity-costs/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nCindy Axne\n",
      "url": "/personalities/cindy-axne/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\u201cZach Nunn took money from Adventureland\u2019s CEO, then sponsored legislation to loosen amusement park safety rules. A child died. Zach Nunn put his big donor first, ahead of the safety of Iowa families.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/18/cindy-axne/blaming-one-legislator-accident-ignores-lot/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nMonica Crowley\n",
      "url": "/personalities/monica-crowley/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nSoviet and Chinese communists have \u201cgrabbed control\u201d of U.S. entertainment, movies, television, music, academia, K-12 education and the news media.\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/17/monica-crowley/pants-fire-claim-communists-have-controlled-us-ins/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nTed Nugent\n",
      "url": "/personalities/ted-nugent/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nThree mass shootings were meant to distract from Hillary Clinton controversies.\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/16/ted-nugent/no-these-mass-shootings-werent-plot-protect-hillar/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nJim Lamon\n",
      "url": "/personalities/jim-lamon/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nBlake Masters \u201cunironically quoted a Nazi, called World War II an unjust war, called the Unabomber one of his intellectual influencers, and shared an article attacking Israel as the North Korea of the Middle East.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/16/jim-lamon/arizona-us-senate-race-attack-ties-masters-nazis-u/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nTed Cruz\n",
      "url": "/personalities/ted-cruz/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\"The impact of President Biden being beholden to the Green New Deal radicals in his party has electricity costs through the roof in Texas.\"\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/21/ted-cruz/green-new-deal-not-blame-high-electricity-costs/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nJoe Biden\n",
      "url": "/personalities/joe-biden/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nThe Supreme Court decision overturning Roe v. Wade \"made the United States an outlier among developed nations in the world\" on abortion rights.\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/24/joe-biden/roe-reversal-ending-national-access-abortion-makes/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nRob Astorino\n",
      "url": "/personalities/rob-astorino/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\u201cWe\u2019ve got a parole board right now that has released 20 cop killers in the last two years under Hochul.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/24/rob-astorino/gop-challenger-overstates-parole-boards-record-und/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nTweets\n",
      "url": "/personalities/tweets/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nRecent research suggests that 15% of abortions are the result of coercion.\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/24/tweets/scant-evidence-15-abortions-are-result-coercion/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nLevar Stoney\n",
      "url": "/personalities/levar-stoney/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\u201cIn Virginia, Black people are eight times (8X) more likely than white people to die of gun homicide.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/24/levar-stoney/virginia-blacks-eight-times-more-likely-whites-be-/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nKevin McCarthy\n",
      "url": "/personalities/kevin-mccarthy/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\u201cAmerican oil is \u2026 more affordable\u201d than foreign oil.\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/24/kevin-mccarthy/kevin-mccarthy-said-domestic-oil-more-affordable-i/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nInstagram posts\n",
      "url": "/personalities/instagram-posts/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nAccording to International Olympic Committee data, \u201can average of 29 athletes under the age of 35 suffered sudden death per year from 1966 to 2004. From March 2021 to March 2022, 769 athletes have died or suffered cardiac arrest.\"\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/23/instagram-posts/claims-connecting-sudden-death-athletes-covid-19-v/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nCatherine Cortez Masto\n",
      "url": "/personalities/catherine-cortez-masto/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nAdam Laxalt \"wants to restrict\" and \"worked to limit access to birth control.\"\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/23/catherine-cortez-masto/gop-nevada-senate-hopeful-adam-laxalt-backed-birth/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nCatherine Cortez Masto\n",
      "url": "/personalities/catherine-cortez-masto/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nAdam Laxalt \"supports eliminating Nevada's protections for legal abortions.\"\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/23/catherine-cortez-masto/gop-senate-hopeful-adam-laxalt-open-tightening-abo/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nLawrence Summers\n",
      "url": "/personalities/lawrence-summers/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n \u201cWhen you have unemployment below 4% and inflation above 4%, recession always follows within two years.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/23/lawrence-summers/fact-checking-larry-summers-formula-unemploymen/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\nRebecca Kleefisch\n",
      "url": "/personalities/rebecca-kleefisch/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\u201cJoe Biden\u2019s margin of the less than 21,000 votes in Wisconsin was the tightest of any state in 2020.\u201d\n",
      "url": "/factchecks/2022/jun/23/rebecca-kleefisch/kleefisch-campaign-wrong-wisconsin-had-smallest-ma/"
    },
